title: Ninja Mountain Bike Performance | Santos (SA020318)
description: Ninja Mountain Bike Performance Skills Clinic
course:
JOIN US CHALLENGING AND FUN 2-DAY CAMP ON SOME OF THE BEST TRAILS IN FLORIDA!

This camp is designed for the enthusiast rider or avid racer that is looking to build up and clean up their ‘toolbox’ of mountain bike skills in order to handle a variety of terrain at speed.
We will blend an in-depth version of our traditional Intermediate / Advanced skills training with coached riding sessions.

title: Simon & Sigalos, LLP presents the 2018 Carlos Laborde Pursuit Cycling
Granfondo Garneau Florida Ride
description: The Granfondo Garneau Florida Ride is a premier road cycling event in South Florida. Built off the tremendous success of the Granfondo Garneau-Quebecor, Louis Garneau, the Canadian road racing olympic champion and cycle-wear manufacturer, has paired up with the Delray Beach Twilight Festival for the sixth year in a row to create an epic cycling experience for the masses!
course: 50 miles along A1A in Palm Beach County,
registration:
The Granfondo Garneau Florida Ride is designed for EVERYONE! Whether you are an experienced cyclist wanting to push your own limits or you are someone new to riding and want to ride at your own pace, the Granfondo Garneau Florida Ride has a perfect ride and group for you. Come discover the Beautiful and Scenic roads of South Florida while being catered to every inch of the way. The event promises to be a day filled with health, wellness, and fun! www.delraygranfondo.com to register. *LIMITED TO 1.000 PARTICIPANTS*
COST: $150 PER RIDER
BEAT THE CLOCK REGISTRATION**
**$150 per Rider: Early registration will cost $100. BEAT THE CLOCK...Registration starts at $100 and will go up to $150 as the event gets closer. Make sure to register early. You never know when the price will change!!!!
notes:
Participants will receive a
commemorative Louis Garneau
Jersey. Made of Diamond Fabric, the jersey has amazing airflow and moisture-wicking properties. Also features a full zip, three back pockets, and an elastic at the heim to mantain positioning. The classic simple styling and technical fabric make this jersey a race favorite.
directions: In downtown Delray Beach, FL. Take 1-95 to Atlantic Blvd. Head east to the water. Park is on the north side of the bridge.
